My name is Sridhar Ranganaboina. I lead the Innovation Pod under CAO Tech in the EP LOB.

Let me get straight to the idea.

What if we could convert any enterprise application into a CLI, Python package, NPM package, SDK, or even an MCP server automatically within a few minutes?

That is exactly what App2Agent does.

The inspiration came from a project I’m currently working on called WebGenie, an autonomous agentic browser. Users can simply give instructions such as:

“Raise an access request for me.”

or

“I’m traveling to Mumbai next week. Find and book the best flight.”

WebGenie can perform these tasks on behalf of the user.

However, while building such agentic systems, we repeatedly encounter three challenges.

First, UI automation. It works, but it introduces latency and can become unstable whenever application screens change.

Second, API integrations. They are reliable, but every integration requires significant business logic, development effort, and ongoing maintenance.

Third, MCP servers. They provide a great agent interface, but most enterprise applications do not have MCP servers readily available today.

This is where App2Agent comes in.

The idea is simple.

Provide your application’s frontend repository as input, and App2Agent automatically analyzes the application, discovers workflows, generates APIs where required, and creates agent-ready interfaces.

Within minutes, it can generate:

• CLI tools
• Python packages
• NPM packages
• Java/Maven SDKs
• MCP servers
• Smart Agent SDKs

But generation is only part of the solution.

App2Agent also automatically tests, validates, and packages these artifacts for enterprise consumption.

On top of that, it provides an App2Agent Hub — a governed marketplace where generated assets can be securely published and consumed by chatbots, AI agents, copilots, and automation platforms across the organization.

In short, App2Agent transforms existing enterprise applications into agent-ready capabilities, dramatically reducing integration effort and accelerating enterprise AI adoption.

Instead of spending weeks building integrations, teams can onboard applications into the agent ecosystem in minutes.

Thank you.
